+
+- Hardened `isSafeRedirect` by matching only exact allowed hostnames or DNS label-bound subdomains after URL parsing.
+- Rejected userinfo, raw backslashes, control characters, localhost, private IPv4 forms normalized by `URL`, IPv6 loopback, IPv6 unique-local, and IPv4-mapped private IPv6 redirects before allowlist matching.
